<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">microservices-observability-stack</code> → SRE proof. WF needs 99% uptime — you have Prometheus/Grafana/Loki/Jaeger stack already built and documented.</p>
