<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>GAPS TO FIX (before submitting to WF)</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Gap 1 — No WF-specific repo exists</strong>
→ Create <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">portfolio-management-erd</code> repo NOW. Add: ERD image (export from this session), README explaining design decisions (why 1-1 Portfolio, why security attributes chosen, what requirements you excluded), tech stack note (Spring Boot backend, React dashboard, PostgreSQL relational DB). One repo = direct proof of systems thinking for WF reviewers.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Gap 2 — event-driven-commerce-platform README doesn't mention financial domain</strong>
